OL,3,CSexual assault survivor shares how a
OL,4,Ccharity helped turn her life around
OL,6,FA sexual assault survivor in the West
OL,7,FCountry has revealed how one charity
OL,8,Fturned her life around.
OL,10,FSARSAS, which stands for Somerset and
OL,11,FAvon Rape and Sexual Abuse Support,
OL,12,Fhelps around 25 people every week. One
OL,13,Fof those people is Liz Roberts.
OL,15,FLiz Roberts reported her brother
OL,16,FAndrew to police for indecently
OL,17,Fassaulting her as a child. She
OL,18,Freceived help from SARSAS immediately.
