OL,3,CSexual assault survivor shares how a
OL,4,Ccharity helped turn her life around
OL,6,FLiz said: "My life hit the floor
OL,7,Freally really hard and without that
OL,8,Fhelping hand, I wouldn't be talking to
OL,9,Fyou today now because that was a major
OL,10,Fstep in my healing.
OL,12,F"I didn't know I needed saving until
OL,13,Fyour life starts to unravel - and then
OL,14,Fyou're drowning, literally, by the day
OL,15,F- and to know and have somebody you
OL,16,Ftrust, you cut through all the small
OL,17,Ftalk."
