OL,3,CSexual assault survivor shares how a
OL,4,Ccharity helped turn her life around
OL,6,FIn 2022, Andrew Herbert was convicted
OL,7,Fof 10 counts of sexual assault against
OL,8,Fhis sister and another underage girl
OL,9,Fin the 1970s.
OL,11,FThe charity now receives around 25
OL,12,Freferrals every week - a steady rise
OL,13,Fsince it was first established 16
OL,14,Fyears ago.
OL,16,FSARSAS says its resources can't keep
OL,17,Fup with growing demand and waiting
OL,18,Flists are getting longer.
