OL,3,CSexual assault survivor shares how a
OL,4,Ccharity helped turn her life around
OL,6,FLorri Weaving, CEO of SARSAS, told ITV
OL,7,FWest Country: "The impacts of sexual
OL,8,Fviolence are devastating - it impacts
OL,9,Fevery area of someone's life - that
OL,10,Ftrauma has a day-to-day impact.
OL,12,F"Many people have waited for a long
OL,13,Ftime to come forward for support. It's
OL,14,Fa really brave thing to do, to pick up
OL,15,Fthat phone and to give us a call and
OL,16,Fto be faced with that wait, it really
OL,17,Fimpacts that trauma.
OL,19,F"We need to be able to support people
OL,20,Fas soon as they come forward."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/6
