OL,3,CSexual assault survivor shares how a
OL,4,Ccharity helped turn her life around
OL,6,FSARSAS says it needs financial help
OL,7,Fquickly. The charity says it will have
OL,8,Fless money because it will pay more
OL,9,Fnational insurance for employees
OL,10,Fbecause of measures outlined in the
OL,11,Flast budget announced by the
OL,12,FGovernment.
OL,14,FLorri said: "Our reliability as a
OL,15,Fcharity to pay employees' national
OL,16,Finsurance as well as for every other
OL,17,Fcharity in the country - it's going to
OL,18,Fhave a real effect on services.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/6
