OL,6,F"So for us, for example, it will cost
OL,7,Fus next year somewhere in the region
OL,8,Fof around #30,000 - which is the
OL,9,Fequivalent of a frontline worker at
OL,10,Fleast.
OL,12,F"Our services will probably reduce and
OL,13,Four waiting lists will go up."
OL,15,FA spokesman from HM Treasury said:
OL,16,F"We've protected small charities by
OL,17,Fmore than doubling the Employment
OL,18,FAllowance to #10,500, meaning more
OL,19,Fthan half of all employers with NICs
OL,20,Fliabilities either gain or see no
OL,21,Fchange next year."
